Subject: drm/exynos: use define instead of default_win member in struct
 mixer_context
Git-commit: a2ee151b6b6863d108552de82e02b77166ca23a8
Patch-mainline: v3.4-rc3

The default_win member in struct mixer_context isn't change its value
after initialized to 0, so it's better using to define.

